                            <comment id="12679249" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Thu, 5 Mar 2009 17:11:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The code for this was in Solr for some time - I just never got around to fixing the bugs, testing and documenting it.  Patch attached.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Examples:&lt;br/&gt;
// relevancy score of the sub-query specified by the qq var (lucene query by default)&lt;br/&gt;
q=query($qq)&amp;amp;qq=+foo +bar baz         &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;// value of the query specified by the qq argument (a dismax query) with a default value of 1.0 for documents that don&apos;t match that query.&lt;br/&gt;
q=query($qq,1)&amp;amp;qq=&lt;/p&gt;
{!dismax qf=myfield pf=myfield}
&lt;p&gt;foo bar       &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;// relevancy score of the lucene query with a default value of 0.1 for any non-matching documents&lt;br/&gt;
query(&lt;/p&gt;
{!lucene v=&apos;body:apple +tag:[* TO *]&apos;}
&lt;p&gt;,0.1)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12679342" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Thu, 5 Mar 2009 20:35:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;ll work on updating the Wiki shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
